com.qbpsimulator.engine.parser.bpmn

Class BPMN2Parser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.qbpsimulator.engine.parser.bpmn.BPMN2Parser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IProcessModelParser
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BPMN2XmlParser

    public abstract class BPMN2Parser
extends Object
implements IProcessModelParser
    This helper class parses BPMN 2.0 files and creates graph representation of the process graph. Note that the implementation uses JDOM, for simplicity and generality.
    Author:
    Madis Abel
